sedalib 1.2.0-SNAPSHOT API

Library for manipulating archives structures and metadata in compliance with SEDA Standard and Vitam implementation (for high-level usage, see the SIPBuilder class).

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.core
Package for SEDA structures management and serialization, deserilization to json and to XML
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.core.json
Package for Jackson json de/serializer of special objects
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.droid
Package for Digital Record Object IDentification(DROID) usage classes.
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.inout
Package for building, importing and exporting archive structure and metadata tools (for high-level usage, see the SIPBuilder class).
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.inout.exporter
Package for tools exporting archive structure and metadata to disk hierarchy, and to SEDA packets SIP
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.inout.importer
Package for tools importing archive structure and metadata from disk hierarchy, and from SEDA packets SIP/DIP
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.metadata
Package for SEDA structure objects (DataObjectPackage, ArchiveUnits and DataObjects) metadata with serialization to and deserilization from XML
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.metadata.namedtype
Package for SEDA generic metadata types, defined by the name of the XML element, with serialization to and deserilization from XML
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.utils
Package for utility classes (exceptions, log...)
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.xml
Package for XML manipulation tools (indent, read, write) using STAX
Library for manipulating archives structures and metadata in compliance with SEDA Standard and Vitam implementation (for high-level usage, see the SIPBuilder class).
